import React from "react"; /** * Pending Friend Request * if there is a pending friend request, then a red dot appears on the sidebar * * mid: 2 boxes * left box is who owes you in green * right box are the people who owe you in red * * list of friends: below spreads 100% width * * button at top to search for people to add as friends * - each person in search results will have the option to "send friend request" or "already friends"(unclickable) * * each friend has 3 dots * if you click the 3 dots, 2 options * a. delete friend => pop up will show if you want to confirm deleting friend * b. add friend to group => pop up will show what groups you are in (on right side of pop up will be * "send invite" or "friend already part of group"(unclickable)) * */ function FriendsScreen() { return (
FriendsScreen
); } export default FriendsScreen;
